    "COMMENTATOR Continued From Page 3 summer French Study Tour were recently com pleted by Wayne State Uni versitys French depart ment The tour will cover 18 cities in England Holland Germany Switzerland and France beginning July 3 and ending August 19 Three weeks in August will be spent at the Uni versity of Grenoble for study of French literature offering two to four hours of academic credit at Wayne State Cost of the allexpense tour is 1363 including tui tion at the University of Grenoble Dr Ediwin Burrows assistant prose ss or of French at Wayne State is the tour leader For information contacts Highland Park Travel Exchange Bureau Inc TO 88788 WSU Presents Annual Religious Series Wayne State Universitys eighth annual This We Believe series will begin with a program on Jud aism Wednesday Feb 27 The series is presented to build understanding among the people of var ious creeds The Univer sitys Councils of Religious Organizations and Religi ous Advisors sponsors the series Chairman of the series is the Rev Robert Wilkie director of Wayne States United Christian Fellow ship The programs are sched uled for 2 pm in the Da vid D Henry Lounge Stu dent Center"
